    "question": "What are the main packges in the model?",
    "durationMs": 87568,
    "status": "OK",
    "finalAnswer": "The main packages in the Thirty Meter Telescope (TMT) model are organized hierarchically:\n\n**Root Package:** TMT\n\n**Main Sub-packages under TMT::Project:**\n1. **Views** - Contains model views and diagrams\n2. **Concerns** - Contains stakeholder concerns\n3. **Management** - Contains project management elements\n4. **Roles** - Contains role definitions\n5. **ViewPoints** - Contains viewpoint definitions\n6. **Components** - Contains system components\n\nThe model follows a structured organization with TMT as the root package, Project as the main container, and these 6 packages representing the primary organizational structure for the telescope system model.",
